---
title: Spring Onion, Sweetcorn & Feta Fritters with Roast Veggie Toss
description: The secret to the success of these moreish veggie fritters is charring the corn in a dry frying pan before mixing them with the other ingredients. It gives an amazing smokey flavour that you won't be able to get enough of.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spring-onion-corn-fetta-fritters-a3aaf74d.jpg
